parameters: Attendant: "I wonder if Luuna-san has safely arrived in Norvania..."

Regnus Grahardt: "This is a thought body. Sorry for appearing like
this."

Attendant: "Oh! Lord Regnus Grahardt! What a transformed appearance!
Have you died and become a spirit? How pitiable!"

Regnus Grahardt: "That's why I said it's an intentional thought
body..."
Attendant: "Just kidding. I understand you have your circumstances."

Attendant: "Do you have business with Lady Rade? No... there are
people looking for you."

Regnus Grahardt: "Yeah. I came here today to give you something
regarding Luuna. I have no business with Rade."
Attendant: "Something for me to pass on?"
Regnus Grahardt: "I want you to give this to Luuna."
Regnus Grahardt: "Luca, I'm counting on you."

Regnus Grahardt: "I can't lend my power right now due to certain
circumstances. Sorry."
